# Design System Guidelines

## 1. Typography & Spacing Hierarchy

### Mobile (≤480px)
- **H1**: 
  - Size: 24px / 1.5rem
  - Margin-bottom: 16px / 1rem
  - Line-height: 1.2
  - Space after: 24px / 1.5rem
- **H2**: 
  - Size: 20px / 1.25rem
  - Margin-bottom: 12px / 0.75rem
  - Line-height: 1.3
  - Space after: 20px / 1.25rem
- **Body**: 
  - Size: 14px / 0.875rem
  - Line-height: 1.5
  - Paragraph spacing: 16px / 1rem

### Tablet (481px–1024px)
- **H1**: 
  - Size: 28px / 1.75rem
  - Margin-bottom: 20px / 1.25rem
  - Line-height: 1.2
  - Space after: 32px / 2rem
- **H2**: 
  - Size: 24px / 1.5rem
  - Margin-bottom: 16px / 1rem
  - Line-height: 1.3
  - Space after: 24px / 1.5rem
- **Body**: 
  - Size: 16px / 1rem
  - Line-height: 1.6
  - Paragraph spacing: 20px / 1.25rem

### Desktop (>1024px)
- **H1**: 
  - Size: 32px / 2rem
  - Margin-bottom: 24px / 1.5rem
  - Line-height: 1.2
  - Space after: 40px / 2.5rem
- **H2**: 
  - Size: 28px / 1.75rem
  - Margin-bottom: 20px / 1.25rem
  - Line-height: 1.3
  - Space after: 32px / 2rem
- **Body**: 
  - Size: 18px / 1.125rem
  - Line-height: 1.6
  - Paragraph spacing: 24px / 1.5rem

## 2. Layout and Container Rules

### Global Container Rules
- **Default max-width**: 1280px (max-w-7xl)
- **Full-width sections**: 100% viewport width
- **Content sections**: max-w-7xl with centered alignment

### Mobile (≤480px)
- **Container padding**: 16px
- **Section spacing**: 32px / 2rem
- **Content width**: 100% (max-w-7xl)
- **Single-column layout**
  - Vertical stack
  - Content margin: 16px

### Tablet (481px–1024px)
- **Container padding**: 24px
- **Section spacing**: 48px / 3rem
- **Content width**: 100% (max-w-7xl)
- **Grid system**: 
  - 12 columns
  - Gutter: 16px
  - 2-column layouts for content

### Desktop (>1024px)
- **Container padding**: 32px
- **Section spacing**: 64px / 4rem
- **Content width**: 100% (max-w-7xl)
- **Grid system**: 
  - 12 columns
  - Gutter: 24px
  - Up to 4-column layouts

## 3. Section Types and Width Rules

### Full-width Sections
- Hero sections
- Background color blocks
- Full-bleed images
- Footer

### Contained Sections (max-w-7xl)
- Main content areas
- Article content
- Card grids
- Feature sections
- Contact forms
- Navigation menus (when not full-width)

